    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/parent": "http://localhost:10000",
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/name": "Transformational Travel Council",
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/description": "# Transformational Travel Council\n\n**Summary:** Global network of tourism professionals committed to regenerative design. The most accessible entry point for Project#079.\n\n---\n\n- **Members:** 200+ across 40+ countries\n- **Cost:** ~$200-500/year\n- **Focus:** Regenerative tourism, transformative travel\n\n## What They Offer\n\n- Real-time WhatsApp group\n- Monthly Coffee + Connect virtual networking\n- Member directory\n- B2B marketplace\n- Spark Talks\n\n## Why First Entry Point\n\n1. Lowest barrier \u2014 $200/year\n2. Active community \u2014 interact immediately\n3. Directly relevant \u2014 retreat facilitators, wellness practitioners\n4. Remote-first \u2014 no travel needed\n\n---\n\n## Connections\n\n- [[0dd852bc-c315-413a-bf37-dc6322cdf748|Connections-First Strategy]]\n- [[6d135887-d90e-4690-9e09-8b56dfe6837d|Project#079 {ED} The Active Venture]]\n- [[c3038639-56fd-4e07-8d4c-d2b81e0a8944|Global Wellness Summit]]"
  },
