    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/parent": "http://localhost:10000",
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/name": "Conscious 500 / Symbiosis",
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/description": "# Conscious 500 / Symbiosis\n\n**Summary:** A global community of 500 conscious leaders. Annual gathering: Symbiosis, Mexico.\n\n---\n\n- Founder: David Giannetto (TEDx, SXSW, Cannes Lions, UN speaker)\n- **Symbiosis**: Mexico, Nov 9-15, 2026, 44 leaders per cohort\n- Audience: C-Level executives, founders\n\n## Themes\n\n- AI meets Consciousness\n- Alignment\n- Harmony\n- Abundance\n\n## Entry Strategy\n\nNot as a participant (~$5-10K). Instead:\n- Apply as a speaker/presenter\n- Connect with David Giannetto via LinkedIn\n- Offer a workshop on the Five-Step System\n\n---\n\n## Connections\n\n- [[0dd852bc-c315-413a-bf37-dc6322cdf748|Connections-First Strategy]]\n- [[6d135887-d90e-4690-9e09-8b56dfe6837d|Project#079 {ED} The Active Venture]]\n- [[7154e6db-cdb0-4f5f-8003-af2eeb32989f|Transformational Travel Council]]"
  },
