    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/parent": "http://localhost:10000",
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/name": "Beyul \u2014 Awakening Leaders Community",
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/description": "# Beyul \u2014 Awakening Leaders Community\n\n**Summary:** Members-only community of awakening leaders. Inspired by the Himalayan beyul tradition.\n\n---\n\n- Philosophy: \u201cA safe space to discover your true nature\u201d\n- Membership: Private, members-only\n- Vibe: Quiet money, deep people\n\n## Offerings\n\n- Transformational Investment Program\n- Beyul Resorts (planned globally)\n- Courses from world-class mentors\n\nBeyul represents the \u201cquiet money\u201d and \u201cdeep people\u201d network \u2014 where serious capital and serious consciousness intersect.\n\n---\n\n## Connections\n\n- [[5b7776af-edf6-4f00-a596-ea82c416c0ca|Conscious 500 / Symbiosis]]\n- [[6d135887-d90e-4690-9e09-8b56dfe6837d|Project#079 {ED} The Active Venture]]\n- [[80910089-f2f8-4c05-891f-d7e19e0b7cdd|The Compiler \u2014 Translating Ancient Wisdom]]\n- [[0dd852bc-c315-413a-bf37-dc6322cdf748|Connections-First Strategy]]"
