    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/parent": "http://localhost:10000",
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/name": "Conscious Island Community \u2014 Tai Nuare",
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/description": "# Conscious Island Community \u2014 Tai Nuare\n\n**Summary:** A 405-acre island in the Caribbean built by followers of Dr. Joe Dispenza\u2019s work. Actively looking for JV partners.\n\n---\n\n- Location: 405-acre Caribbean island\n- Status: 16 adjacent properties acquired, active community\n- Built by followers of Dr. Joe Dispenza\n\n## Partnership Opportunities\n\n- Wellness Center\n- Enterprise partnerships\n- Equity exchange\n- Crowdfunding\n- Co-creation\n\n## Strategic Importance\n\nThis is the most concrete zero-capital prototype opportunity:\n\n> **Our IP** (Pattern Paradigm retreat framework) + **Their land** (405-acre island) = **Prototype retreat**\n\n---\n\n## Connections\n\n- [[0dd852bc-c315-413a-bf37-dc6322cdf748|Connections-First Strategy]]\n- [[6d135887-d90e-4690-9e09-8b56dfe6837d|Project#079 {ED} The Active Venture]]\n- [[ff6be8b0-a3d8-45a6-8116-ee9cc313861e|5D Ventures \u2014 Progression of Consciousness Fund]]\n- [[82641244-44a9-414b-b51a-4a02ee2f3ac8|Dimensions Retreats \u2014 The Blueprint]]"
  },
