    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/parent": "http://localhost:10000",
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/name": "Unity Earth \u2014 Regenerative Community Network",
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/description": "# Unity Earth \u2014 Regenerative Community Network\n\n**Summary:** A nodal network of regenerative community hubs worldwide. Physical flagship in Peru\u2019s Sacred Valley.\n\n---\n\n- Flagship: UnityHub Peru (Sacred Valley)\n- Network: Global community of conscious entrepreneurs\n\n## Offerings\n\n- Coworking residencies\n- Retreats\n- Events\n- Online community\n- Masterminds\n\n## Strategic Relevance\n\n- Remote participation first\n- Distributed network\n- Aligned ethos \u2014 regenerative, conscious, community-focused\n- Sacred Valley is a natural pilot market\n\n---\n\n## Connections\n\n- [[0dd852bc-c315-413a-bf37-dc6322cdf748|Connections-First Strategy]]\n- [[6d135887-d90e-4690-9e09-8b56dfe6837d|Project#079 {ED} The Active Venture]]\n- [[7154e6db-cdb0-4f5f-8003-af2eeb32989f|Transformational Travel Council]]"
