    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/parent": "http://localhost:10000",
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/name": "Orion Retreats Mastermind",
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/description": "# Orion Retreats Mastermind\n\n**Summary:** Mastermind community for retreat creators. A direct peer group of people who have already built retreat businesses.\n\n---\n\n- For: Coaches, healers, facilitators building retreat businesses\n- Format: In-person mastermind retreats\n\n## Member Statistics\n\n- Average revenue per retreat: $25K\n- Typical frequency: 4-6 retreats annually\n- Total annual income potential: $100K-$150K+\n\n## Strategic Value\n\nThis is the operational peer group. Join to:\n- Validate pricing assumptions\n- Find co-facilitators\n- Learn operational best practices\n- Test the Pattern Paradigm with experienced peers\n\n---\n\n## Connections\n\n- [[0dd852bc-c315-413a-bf37-dc6322cdf748|Connections-First Strategy]]\n- [[6d135887-d90e-4690-9e09-8b56dfe6837d|Project#079 {ED} The Active Venture]]\n- [[7154e6db-cdb0-4f5f-8003-af2eeb32989f|Transformational Travel Council]]"
