    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/parent": "http://localhost:10000",
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/name": "Global Wellness Summit",
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/description": "# Global Wellness Summit\n\n**Summary:** The premier global gathering for the wellness industry. Location: Phuket, Thailand, November 10-13, 2026.\n\n---\n\n- The premier global wellness industry gathering\n- Location: Phuket, Thailand\n- Dates: November 10-13, 2026\n- 50+ countries, top business leaders and investors\n\n## Features\n\n- Main conference with keynotes and panels\n- Shark Tank of Wellness competition\n- Networking with industry leaders\n\n## Strategic Value\n\n**HIGH FIT** \u2014 This is where the wellness industry\u2019s decision-makers gather.\n\nEven attending as a delegate is valuable for market intelligence, networking, and validation.\n\n---\n\n## Connections\n\n- [[ff6be8b0-a3d8-45a6-8116-ee9cc313861e|5D Ventures \u2014 Progression of Consciousness Fund]]\n- [[6d8f5a63-1635-45f6-84ba-744424a94d9d|Conscious Island Community \u2014 Tai Nuare]]\n- [[6d135887-d90e-4690-9e09-8b56dfe6837d|Project#079 {ED} The Active Venture]]\n- [[7154e6db-cdb0-4f5f-8003-af2eeb32989f|Transformational Travel Council]]\n- [[67aa53bd-17e8-43e3-a7ce-e944650529a5|Spark Tank \u2014 Wellness Founder Competition]]"
  },
