    ],
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/parent": "http://localhost:10000",
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/name": "5D Ventures \u2014 Progression of Consciousness Fund",
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/description": "# 5D Ventures \u2014 Progression of Consciousness Fund\n\n**Summary:** Venture philanthropy firm at the intersection of venture capital and philanthropy. The most aligned capital source found.\n\n---\n\nInvests in businesses that deepen connection to nature, spirit, and each other.\n\n## Three Initiatives\n\n1. **Progression of Consciousness Fund** \u2014 Private equity for retreat centres\n2. **Resilient World Trust** \u2014 Land acquisition and regeneration\n3. **5D Angel** \u2014 Microlending, incubation\n\n## Portfolio\n\n| Company | Investment |\n|---------|-----------|\n| Dimensions Retreats | $3.2M co-founded |\n| Holos Global | Portfolio |\n| Othership | Portfolio |\n| Abroad.io | Portfolio |\n\nWhy this is the most aligned source: explicit consciousness mandate, retreat focus, portfolio synergy, multiple entry points.\n\n---\n\n## Connections\n\n- [[82641244-44a9-414b-b51a-4a02ee2f3ac8|Dimensions Retreats \u2014 The Blueprint]]\n- [[439c1232-556c-4523-8c01-604b79d20804|Othership \u2014 Social Wellness Sanctuary]]\n- [[0df64b0e-a94d-4454-a64e-43ad21dfd53f|Holos Global \u2014 Transformative Retreat Center]]\n- [[a8c423e2-1522-4d35-857a-690391d120ed|Abroad.io \u2014 Purpose-Led Travel]]\n- [[0dd852bc-c315-413a-bf37-dc6322cdf748|Connections-First Strategy]]\n- [[6d135887-d90e-4690-9e09-8b56dfe6837d|Project#079 {ED} The Active Venture]]"
  },
  {
    "@id": "http://localhost:10000/82641244-44a9-414b-b51a-4a02ee2f3ac8",
