      "https://atomicdata.dev/classes/Document"
    ],
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/parent": "http://localhost:10000",
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/name": "Dimensions Retreats",
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/description": "# Dimensions Retreats\n\n**Summary:** Luxury wellness destination in Algonquin Highlands, Ontario. 5D Ventures co-founded and lead investor ($3,219,000).\n\n---\n\n- Location: Algonquin Highlands, Ontario, Canada\n- Focus: Plant medicine, somatic psychotherapy, neuroscience\n- Investors: 5D Ventures ($3,219,000 lead)\n- Research partner: Queen\u2019s University for psychedelic research\n\n## Why the Blueprint\n\n1. Luxury + Evidence-based + Consciousness \u2014 the exact triad\n2. Academic partnership lends credibility\n3. HNWI target \u2014 high-ticket, high-impact\n4. 5D Ventures backing validates the model\n\n> Could the Pattern Paradigm retreat be a new program track WITHIN Dimensions Retreats\u2019 existing infrastructure?\n\n---\n\n## Connections\n\n- [[ff6be8b0-a3d8-45a6-8116-ee9cc313861e|5D Ventures \u2014 Progression of Consciousness Fund]]\n- [[6d135887-d90e-4690-9e09-8b56dfe6837d|Project#079 {ED} The Active Venture]]\n- [[6d8f5a63-1635-45f6-84ba-744424a94d9d|Conscious Island Community \u2014 Tai Nuare]]"
  },
