    ],
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/parent": "http://localhost:10000",
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/name": "Othership \u2014 Social Wellness Sanctuary",
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/description": "# Othership \u2014 Social Wellness Sanctuary\n\n**Summary:** Modern bathhouse and social wellness sanctuary. Sauna, ice bath, breathwork. 5D Ventures portfolio company.\n\n---\n\n- Offerings: Sauna, ice bath, breathwork\n- Focus: Nervous system regulation, emotional processing\n- Model: Repeatable, scalable, community-driven\n\n## Relevance\n\n- Proof that social wellness is commercially viable\n- Othership participants are natural audience for deeper retreat work\n- Their short-form nervous system work \u2014 our long-form transformation\n\n> Othership gets people in the door. The Pattern Paradigm retreat is the deep end.\n\n---\n\n## Connections\n\n- [[ff6be8b0-a3d8-45a6-8116-ee9cc313861e|5D Ventures \u2014 Progression of Consciousness Fund]]\n- [[6d135887-d90e-4690-9e09-8b56dfe6837d|Project#079 {ED} The Active Venture]]"
