    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/parent": "http://localhost:10000",
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/name": "Holos Global \u2014 Transformative Retreat Center",
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/description": "# Holos Global \u2014 Transformative Retreat Center\n\n**Summary:** Transformative retreat center focused on plant medicine, regenerative agriculture, and holistic living. 5D Ventures portfolio.\n\n---\n\n- Focus: Plant medicine, regenerative agriculture\n- Tone: Community-oriented, heart-centered\n- 5D Ventures portfolio company\n\n## Strategic Relevance\n\n- Different prototype context than Dimensions\n- Potential lower-cost pilot (less luxury overlay)\n- Community-building expertise\n- Regenerative agriculture as retreat component\n\n---\n\n## Connections\n\n- [[ff6be8b0-a3d8-45a6-8116-ee9cc313861e|5D Ventures \u2014 Progression of Consciousness Fund]]\n- [[82641244-44a9-414b-b51a-4a02ee2f3ac8|Dimensions Retreats \u2014 The Blueprint]]\n- [[6d135887-d90e-4690-9e09-8b56dfe6837d|Project#079 {ED} The Active Venture]]"
