    ],
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/parent": "http://localhost:10000",
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/name": "Abroad.io \u2014 Purpose-Led Experiential Travel",
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/description": "# Abroad.io \u2014 Purpose-Led Experiential Travel\n\n**Summary:** Purpose-led experiential travel company. 5D Ventures portfolio company.\n\n---\n\n- Focus: Indigenous wisdom, deep human connection\n- Model: Curated transformative travel experiences\n- 5D Ventures portfolio company\n\n## Strategic Value\n\nAbroad.io is a **distribution channel**:\n- They curate experiences for travelers seeking depth\n- Their audience aligns with the Pattern Paradigm target\n- Existing 5D Ventures connection facilitates introduction\n\n> Would Abroad.io list a Pattern Paradigm retreat? Revenue share?\n\n---\n\n## Connections\n\n- [[ff6be8b0-a3d8-45a6-8116-ee9cc313861e|5D Ventures \u2014 Progression of Consciousness Fund]]\n- [[6d135887-d90e-4690-9e09-8b56dfe6837d|Project#079 {ED} The Active Venture]]\n- [[82641244-44a9-414b-b51a-4a02ee2f3ac8|Dimensions Retreats \u2014 The Blueprint]]"
  },
