    ],
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/parent": "http://localhost:10000",
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/name": "Wellness Sanctuary Fund",
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/description": "# Wellness Sanctuary Fund\n\n**Summary:** Real estate fund acquiring boutique hotels for wellness sanctuaries. 18-22% IRR target.\n\n---\n\n- Strategy: Acquire and transform hotels into wellness sanctuaries\n- Locations: Guatemala, Costa Rica, Peru, Colombia, Panama\n- Target returns: 18-22% IRR\n\n## Strategic Relevance\n\nThey own the physical infrastructure Project#079 needs.\nThey need programming. The Pattern Paradigm could be their signature retreat program.\n\nThis is real estate capital, not venture capital. If the Pattern Paradigm drives bookings, they become a natural partner.\n\n---\n\n## Connections\n\n- [[ff6be8b0-a3d8-45a6-8116-ee9cc313861e|5D Ventures \u2014 Progression of Consciousness Fund]]\n- [[6d135887-d90e-4690-9e09-8b56dfe6837d|Project#079 {ED} The Active Venture]]\n- [[6d8f5a63-1635-45f6-84ba-744424a94d9d|Conscious Island Community \u2014 Tai Nuare]]"
