    ],
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/parent": "http://localhost:10000",
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/name": "The Gamechangers Middle East",
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/description": "# The Gamechangers Middle East\n\n**Summary:** Dubai-based investment reality show.\n\n---\n\n- Format: TV investment reality series\n- Location: Dubai, UAE\n- Focus: High-growth startups\n\n## Wellness Precedents\n\n- Shake Your Plants: AED 1.2M + AED 2M credit line for 20% equity\n- Exhale (corporate mental health): Pitched for AED 1M (no deal)\n\n## Fit\n\n**MODERATE FIT** \u2014 Wellness is active but they favor:\n- Consumer products over experience/IP models\n- Scalable tech-enabled businesses\n- UAE-focused ventures\n\n---\n\n## Connections\n\n- [[6d135887-d90e-4690-9e09-8b56dfe6837d|Project#079 {ED} The Active Venture]]\n- [[c3038639-56fd-4e07-8d4c-d2b81e0a8944|Global Wellness Summit]]\n- [[67aa53bd-17e8-43e3-a7ce-e944650529a5|Spark Tank \u2014 Wellness Founder Competition]]"
  },
  {
    "@id": "http://localhost:10000/67aa53bd-17e8-43e3-a7ce-e944650529a5",
