    ],
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/parent": "http://localhost:10000",
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/name": "Spark Tank \u2014 Wellness Founder Competition",
    "https://atomicdata.dev/properties/description": "# Spark Tank \u2014 Wellness Founder Competition\n\n**Summary:** Live pitch competition for wellness founders. Tempe, Arizona, October 1, 2026.\n\n---\n\n- Format: Live pitch competition\n- For: Wellness founders, retreat leaders, practitioners\n- Location: Tempe, Arizona\n- Date: October 1, 2026\n- Includes: 3-day retreat + 90-day integration support\n\n## Fit\n\n**HIGH FIT** \u2014 Directly targets retreat leaders.\nThe 3-day retreat format mirrors what Project#079 would offer.\n\n## Strategy\n\nPrepare a 5-minute pitch: Pattern Paradigm as unique IP, HNWI target market, Conscious Island prototype opportunity. Network with judges and fellow founders.\n\n---\n\n## Connections\n\n- [[0dd852bc-c315-413a-bf37-dc6322cdf748|Connections-First Strategy]]\n- [[6d135887-d90e-4690-9e09-8b56dfe6837d|Project#079 {ED} The Active Venture]]\n- [[c3038639-56fd-4e07-8d4c-d2b81e0a8944|Global Wellness Summit]]\n- [[f32c284e-5eea-4382-9d1d-6fe86fb7c84e|The Gamechangers Middle East]]"
